TITLE: Using getUnsafeWindow in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use getUnsafeWindow to access the unsandboxed window object in userscripts for dispatching events that might be rejected by websites.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Sv443-Network/UserUtils/blob/main/docs.md#2025-04-16_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { getUnsafeWindow } from "@sv443-network/userutils";

// trick the site into thinking the mouse was moved:
